description:
Deadpool is BACK....and so is Wolverine! And they're both in the MCU now! Sounds like a lot to unpack, but don't worry, this is a SPOILER FREE review, so I'll unpack none of it, and be as vague as possible. Here's my review for DEADPOOL & WOLVERINE!

#Deadpool #DeadpoolAndWolverine
title: Deadpool & Wolverine - Movie Review
